output_big_8 = io.BytesIO(struct.pack('>%sd' % self.test_array.size, *self.
    test_array.flatten('C')))
targetarray, headers, extraCaptures = oommfdecode._binaryDecode(filehandle=
    output_big_8, chunksize=self.chunksize_8, decoder=struct.Struct('>d'),
    targetarray=self.outArray, headers=self.headers, extraCaptures=self.
    extraCaptures)
np.testing.assert_allclose(targetarray, 2.0 * self.test_array)
